description: Do you need a fun way to cool off on a hot SoCal day? Then it sounds like you need Kona Ice! Kona Ice La Jolla is serving up the best shaved ice you'll ever have! Cool and refreshing is the name of the game and nobody does it better than Kona Ice. Flavored just how you like, Kona Ice is perfect for everyone! So keep an eye out for this fantastically frozen good time today!
name: Kona Ice La Jolla
